## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/sympathyAI.git
cd sympathyAI
pip install -e .
```

No external dependencies required for the heuristic pipeline.

For LLM-as-judge coherence scoring:
```bash
pip install -e ".[llm]"
```

